Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest page

Purpose:
  Read one archive object by id.

Usage:
  spinedigest page <archive.sdpub> <id> [--json]

Contract:
  - Mutates: no.
  - LLM: no.
  - JSON: yes.
  - For sourced chapters without summaries, prints source preview and fragment ids.

Examples:
  spinedigest page book.sdpub chapter:1
  spinedigest page book.sdpub fragment:1:0
  spinedigest page book.sdpub node:84
